    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now lets get started...</strong></p><p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>diced chicken breast</strong> and <strong>bacon lardons</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to brown</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
