    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>waxy potatoes</strong> to a heatproof bowl, then cover with <strong>cling film</strong> and pierce a few holes in the top with a fork</p><p>Put the bowl in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 6-8 min or until the potatoes are fork-tender</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
