    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim your<strong> green beans</strong>, then add them to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cook for 3-4 min or until tender with a bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain and return to the pot and keep covered until serving</p>",
