    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Once browned, crumble your <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong> into the pan with the chicken and bacon and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
