      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms have softened, add your <strong>onion marmalade</strong> to the pan with your <strong>soft cheese</strong>, <strong>cornflour</strong>, <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good stir and cook for 4 min or until the sauce begins to thicken and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>creamy chicken, bacon & mushroom stew</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
