        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are tender, add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>and<strong> </strong>roughly crush with a fork – these are your <strong>crushed potatoes</strong></p><p>Roughly tear your <strong>parsley</strong> into the creamy chicken, bacon & mushroom stew and season with a generous grind of <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
